name: Window to Avalon Harbor
description:
From inside the shady covered walkway of Via Casino, this window view of recreational boats in the Avalon Harbor invites you to step out and enjoy the bright sunny day. One of many enticing views on Catalina Island, off the coast of CA.

#1 in the "Inviting You Through" series, a collection of windows and covered passages, which will invite you to look or travel through them, to see what's on the other side, or simply enjoy the journey of getting there.
